snippet.title: Escape From Lesco - Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
GoFundMe ► https://gofund.me/3e3bb7b9

Escape From Lesco is a first person psychological horror game developed by Jwiky (Me)

This isn't your usual shift... What would you do if you were trapped inside of a supermarket at night, where you can't help but feel that your being watched... 

Thanks for Watching! :D. If you can subscribe then please do :]

Join My Discord To Appear In Future Videos:
